# voice-loom-bot — töö kontekst

## Projekt
- **Frontend / admin:** Vite + React (`src/`, sh `CreateAgent.tsx`).
- **Orchestrator (backend kõned):** `orchestrator/` — Twilio Media Streams ↔ OpenAI Realtime; IIZI combined reg+location SMS inbound voog.

## IIZI “brain”
- **Admin seaded:** `settings.brainUi` (Deterministic Flow Controls) — `src/types/brainUiSettings.ts`; salvestamine: täissalvestus `settingsPayload` sisaldab `...rawAgentSettings` + `brainUi`; eraldi nupp merge’ib `{ ...existingSettings, brainUi }`.
- **Runtime:** `orchestrator/src/brain/agentBrainUiTypes.ts` — `resolveRuntimeBrainUiFromSettings`, `DEFAULT_RUNTIME_BRAIN_UI_SETTINGS` (sh `conflictBehavior: ask_clarification`).
- **Tööriistaväravad / SMS:** `orchestrator/src/brain/agent-brain.ts` + kombineeritud SMS intent-värav ka `media-stream.ts` (`gateIiziCombinedSms`).
- **Intent merge:** `orchestrator/src/flow/iiziBrainMerge.ts` (legacy 2 arg vs poliitika opts); olek `orchestrator/src/flow/iiziBrain.ts` (`runtimeBrainUi`, `recomputeFinalIntent`).

## Tavad
- Ära kirjuta üle kogu `agents.settings`; säilita `...existing` / `rawAgentSettings` spread.
- Kasutaja eelistab vastuseid **eesti keeles**.
- Deploy / push ainult kui kasutaja palub.

## Testid (orchestrator)
```bash
cd orchestrator && npm run typecheck && npm run intent-classify-smoke
```
